    <item>
      <title>Portable Power Stations Under $500</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/gear/portable-power-stations-under-500/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Jan 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/gear/portable-power-stations-under-500/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;If you want plug-and-play power without a full electrical build, these units offer the best value for everyday van life.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Top Budget Power Stations&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;top-budget-power-stations&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#top-budget-power-stations&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;EcoFlow RIVER 2 Pro&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;ecoflow-river-2-pro&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#ecoflow-river-2-pro&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: fast recharge, lightweight, reliable app.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: premium pricing during non-sale periods.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Check EcoFlow Price&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;BLUETTI EB55&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;bluetti-eb55&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#bluetti-eb55&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: good port variety, solid battery life.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: heavier than similar-capacity models.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;View BLUETTI Deals&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Jackery Explorer 300 Plus&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;jackery-explorer-300-plus&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#jackery-explorer-300-plus&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: compact and beginner-friendly.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: lower output for power-hungry appliances.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;Shop Jackery 300 Plus&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&#xA;&lt;h3 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Anker SOLIX C800 (sale-dependent under $500)&#xA;    &lt;div id=&#34;anker-solix-c800-sale-dependent-under-500&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;    &lt;span&#xA;        class=&#34;absolute top-0 w-6 transition-opacity opacity-0 -start-6 not-prose group-hover:opacity-100 select-none&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;a class=&#34;text-primary-300 dark:text-neutral-700 !no-underline&#34; href=&#34;#anker-solix-c800-sale-dependent-under-500&#34; aria-label=&#34;Anchor&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/span&gt;&#xA;    &#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Pros: high output for cost, good brand support.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Cons: often near the top of the budget cap.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;CTA: &lt;a href=&#34;&#34; &gt;See Latest Anker Offer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
      
